headline: New Report Shows Employee Retention Outranks Almost Everything Else as U.S. Employers Tackle Burnout
summary: In a workplace climate shaped by economic uncertainty, Gallagher's 2025 U.S. Talent Benchmarks Report reveals that employee retention has become a top operational priority — ranking second only to growing revenue or sales.
